features
    AIAssistant {abstract}
        mandatory
            Model
                alternative
                    GPT4o {cost 8, tokens "128k"}
                    Gemini {cost 10, tokens "1M"}
                    Claude {cost 9, tokens "200k"}
            Plan
                alternative
                    Free {monthLimit 50}
                    Premium {monthLimit 1000}
            Access {abstract}
                or
                    WebApp
                    API {cost 2}
        optional
            FineTuning {cost 5}
            Integer Temperature
            ImageGeneration
            WebSearch
constraints
    ImageGeneration => GPT4 | Gemini
    API => !WebSearch
    FineTuning <=> Premium
    Temperature >= 0 & Temperature <= 5
    sum(Cost) < 15